data.description:
This beautiful home boasts 2 story foyer that leads into large great room with fireplace. Kitchen is open to breakfast nook and great room and features stainless steel appliances, gorgeous cabinets and pantry.All bedrooms are upstairs as well as laundry.Master suite is very large with walk in closet and master bath features dual vanity,separate shower and garden tub.Enjoy the benefits of fitness centers,clubhouse and swimming pools.Take advantage of lender credit of 1% to use for buying down point or whatever you like Contact Justin Price for details https://www.mottomortgage.com/offices/strategic-sanford/justinprice/
New flooring Downstairs. And now offering $3,000.00 in seller concessions to use as you choose!!!!!
